# Documentation language

All documentation in this repository must be written in **English**.

This includes:

- Files under `docs/`
- Root-level markdown (`README.md`, `CHANGELOG.md`, guides, test plans)
- AI integration guides and Cursor rules that describe dbAPI for other projects
- Comments in markdown meant for human readers (prose, not code identifiers)

Do not write documentation in other languages unless the user explicitly requests a translation of existing English docs.
